  * Improved package build
  * Support for Fedora
  * Removed GtkBuilder support for compatibility with more distributions
  * Memory and stability improvements

meiga (0.3.1) - Sun, 01 Nov 2009 00:36:38 +0200

  * Fixed GtkBuilder ui file and deprecated old Glade file
  * Changed private properties to Vala property assignation
  * Enhanced HTML headers
  * Added pending/total transfers counter

meiga (0.3.0) - Sat, 03 Oct 2009 01:49:00 +0200

  * Context menus for Nautilus and Konqueror
  * Prevent server operation until a GUI has been registered
  * Fixed bug: Use proper syntax for gupnp calls depending on the version
	detected
  * Redirection process is now asynchronous by using threads
  * Ssh redirection backend
  * DISPLAY environment variable forwarded to MeigaServer

